<h2>Requirements for the Minor</h2>
<p><span class="diffadded" id="htmldiff0" title="Added content">Students must complete 15 semester hours (five courses) as outlined below.</span> A minimum cumulative GPA of 2.50/4.00 is required for admission to the minor. A GPA of 2.50/4.00 is required in the courses taken towards the minor.</p>
